results.name: Where n-th prime occurs in A111267.
maple: A111267 := proc(nmin) local a,k,qn,dvs; a := [1] ; qn := 5 ; while nops(a) < nmin do dvs := sort([op(numtheory[divisors](qn))]) ; for k from 1 to nops(dvs) do if not dvs[k] in a then a := [op(a),dvs[k]] ; qn := qn+ithprime(nops(a)+1) ; break ; fi ; od ; od; RETURN(a) ; end: A111272 := proc(nmin) local a,a111267,n,i; a := [] ; a111267 := A111267(nmin) ; n := 1; while member( ithprime(n),a111267,'i') do a := [op(a),i] ; n := n+1 ; od; RETURN(a) ; end: A111272(1000) ; # _R. J. Mathar_, Aug 20 2007
